  4,23,"Yג€™abra mo (s־µ mob־µware) mo maamenom, ne mo mma mmaa, ne monua mmaa, ne mosewaanom, ne mo maame nua mmaa, ne monua mmarima mma mmaa, ne mo nua mmaa mma mmaa, ne mo maamenom a wֽ»n ama mo nufoֽ» anom, ne monua mmaa a (monfri eni anaas־µ sekorֽ» na mmom) mone wֽ»n anom nufu korֽ», ne moyere nom maamenom, ne momma nnoma mmaa a mona mohw־µ wֽ»n soֽ» a wֽ»ג€™y־µ moyere nom a moakֽ» wֽ»n ho mma mmaa; nas־µ monkֽ»ֽ» wֽ»n (maame) ho de־µ a, ־µne־µ bֽ»ne biara nni moso; ־µna mo mma mmarima a wֽ»ג€™firi moara mosisi mu yere nom. (Yג€™abra mo nso) s־µ mob־µka nnua mmaa mmienu abom (aware wֽ»n), gyes־µ de־µ atwa mu. Nokor־µ s־µ, Nyankopֽ»n ne Bֽ»nefaky־µ Hene, na ֶ†ne Mmֽ»borֽ»hunu Hene"
